This is a mediaplayer which using txplayer to play videos.

How To Use:

1. Using eclipse to open "txmediaplayer"、"txmediawidget"、"txpalyer" three android projects.

2. in project "txplayer", open file "com.taixin.ffmpeg.demo.txplayer.java", find "mVideoPath" and replace it with your video path.

3. Then run it.

